dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase NSheboygan_Roads_2018.gdbN. [Road segments representing centerlines of all roadways or carriageways in Sheboygan County. Typically, this information is compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the road centerlines support address geocoding and mapping. It also serves as a source for public works and other agencies that are responsible for the active management of the road network.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
